*   **Dynamic AI Kit Generation:** The "Gen Kit" feature is no longer limited to a single style. It now prompts you to describe the kind of drum kit you want (e.g., "lo-fi house," "80s synthwave," "heavy metal"), and the AI will generate appropriate sounds and patterns based on your input.
